snippet.title: Astro Assembler Level 1
snippet.description: I purchased this game from Circuit City when I was really little, played it on Windows XP. After some practice, here is my best play through of level 1 on Windows 10, recording it with Windows game bar. I'm sorry the first minute is bad quality, it gets better.
